{
  "stem": "19441.6",
  "chunk_idx": 9,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 11.9,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 73,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And you will do what you want anyway.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 74,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] He did like that.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 74,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Oh, go away, he says.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 74,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And he put the revolver in.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 74,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And that all-- the commander and that-- all they saw, saw my prestige went higher.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 74,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And so many things I could do which I wouldn't be able to if I wouldn't be so outspoken, daring.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 74,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "Because I said, only once I am going to the chimney.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 74,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "But till I go, I do everything in the good of the people.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 74,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "Even if it's dangerous.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 75,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I would let him take one?",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 76,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "To send them to the gas chambers.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 77,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yeah.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 77,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Yeah.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 78,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Because-- because he was-- he didn't have any sanatorium.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 78,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "He didn't have anything.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 78,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "He wasn't a top doctor.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 78,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "He was just [YIDDISH].",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 79,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I was about at-- September, let's say, about six months, eh?",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 80,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "'44.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 80,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "The camp finished.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 80,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And imagine, that shows you, the commander came to pick me up.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 80,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And he said, come with me.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 80,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Now I show you how hard you were going to work and how hard you will have it.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 80,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And I said, like all other Jews.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 80,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "Now we will have it even harder.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 80,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "So it's my fate.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 80,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "I can't change it.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 80,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "So-- And he was teasing me that till we arrived to the kitchen in Birkenau.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 80,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "He came to the kitchen and there was the SS woman in charge.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 80,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And she said-- and he said, here I bring you the kapo of the kitchen.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 80,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS]",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 81,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So I was thinking there is a kapo.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 81,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Because you know everything beforehand, when I was in Birkenau.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 81,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Kapo of the kitchen was a German woman, who was a lesbian friend of the lageralteste, of the German lageralteste.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 82,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "The German lageralteste was very good to the Jews and sympathetic.",
      "word_count": 11
    }
  ],
